<div class="home-content">
    <h2>Welcome to the Indie Game Jam Manager</h2>
    <p>This web application helps manage indie game jams, including participants, teams, games, and tools.</p>

    <div class="entity-links">
        <div class="entity-card">
            <h3>Game Jams</h3>
            <p>Manage game jam events, dates, locations, and team size limits.</p>
            <div class="card-actions">
                <a href="/jams" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Jams</a>
                <a href="/jams/add" class="btn btn-secondary">Add New Jam</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="entity-card">
            <h3>Participants</h3>
            <p>Manage individual participants with their skills and contact information.</p>
            <div class="card-actions">
                <a href="/participants" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Participants</a>
                <a href="/participants/add" class="btn btn-secondary">Add New Participant</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="entity-card">
            <h3>Teams</h3>
            <p>Organize participants into teams for specific game jams.</p>
            <div class="card-actions">
                <a href="/teams" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Teams</a>
                <a href="/teams/add" class="btn btn-secondary">Add New Team</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="entity-card">
            <h3>Games</h3>
            <p>Track games submitted to jams with scores, engines, and genres.</p>
            <div class="card-actions">
                <a href="/games" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Games</a>
                <a href="/games/add" class="btn btn-secondary">Add New Game</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="entity-card">
            <h3>Tools</h3>
            <p>Catalog development tools used in game creation.</p>
            <div class="card-actions">
                <a href="/tools" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Tools</a>
                <a href="/tools/add" class="btn btn-secondary">Add New Tool</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="entity-card">
            <h3>Game Participants</h3>
            <p>Assign participants to games and define their roles.</p>
            <div class="card-actions">
                <a href="/game-participants" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Game Participants</a>
                <a href="/game-participants/add" class="btn btn-secondary">Add New Assignment</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="entity-card">
            <h3>Game Tools</h3>
            <p>Track which tools were used for each game.</p>
            <div class="card-actions">
                <a href="/game-tools" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Game Tools</a>
                <a href="/game-tools/add" class="btn btn-secondary">Add New Tool Usage</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
